## Orchestration Offloading

### Problem
Most agent sessions are automated overhead (witness, refinery, patrol).
These are mechanical tasks that don't need top-tier reasoning.

### Solution
Route patrol agents through LiteLLM proxy to cheaper backends.

### Environment Variables
```bash
ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=${LITELLM_URL}  # LiteLLM proxy
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=<litellm-key>    # Key with model aliases
```

### Configure Per-Role
In `city.toml`:
```toml
[role_env.witness]
ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL = "${LITELLM_URL}"
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY = "<litellm-patrol-key>"

[role_env.refinery]
ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL = "${LITELLM_URL}"
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY = "<litellm-patrol-key>"
```
{{ end }}
